::Skulletron::

	Skulletron immediatley heard Rex and Firearm tell him to get into robot
mode.  Oh ya!  If he didn't, this intruder would get away.  He transformed,
grabbed the cuffs and walked over to BrightBlade.

	"I'm taking you into custody now!" He said as he put the cuffs on
BrightBlade, chuckling and waiting to see how BrightBlade would react to
her thoughts.
